you ever - if - for - he would go round the schools and get the absentees names you see. And he went round and inquired for the homes why you weren't in the school. But of course if there was children playing truant and children should h}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15487441\charrsid10313804 ave been at school and they saw}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804  {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Daddy{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Lake{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, they got to keep out of his road because he would just collar them. He was {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Daddy{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Lake{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 in these days. He would collar them - and find out - and he went round to know why they werenae at the school. And what was it you asked me before that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 Are you sorry about anything about your education?
