Well, I think - that - if I - had been - I think I would have been quite clever enough. I think I was inclined - when we were kept down at home maybe to - to - take a chance when you're 
outside, you know, the school. That - I can remember - Mr Duncan, he was a great disciplinarian but he was awful - he was fair. Well - I can remember I'd been having - doing some mischief amongst - the other girls this day. And we were at drill. We were g
e
tting drill at this time. And his room, the doors opened up, and he was the - he was second in command you see and - he took - to do with all of it. And unseen to me, I had been capering with some other of the girls, I was in the fourth standard then - an
d all of a sudden this calling - Winifred Bridges. When I get you into my room I'll - he never had cause, never. Oh dear me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 How long did you stay at this school?
