Oh it was really, there was - there was - that - that - that was no such thing, it was just - there wa
s the dirty boys that you didna like. There was the boys in a - in a class that you didna like. Oh no, there was nae such thing as swearing. There was the - and the boys that you steered clear of that you know - they was the nasty boys, girls knew they di
dnaw - they used - they didna like certain boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 You weren't allowed to join in grown ups conversations were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6565549 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 No. Oh no. But - no, you never interfered, oh no, how never -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 If you did something that they disapproved of what would happen, 
