No, you see - that - that girl - well - the chap was a Roman Catholic and she was having the baby to which - nae - the Catholic wouldnae want her, and her people wouldnae want the Catholics, so there you are.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 They would rather she had a child without being married?
