Oh yes, it was only St Patrick's Day they did this. But - but again - there was - Catholics were Catholics and you were Protestants, there was either - you didna - you didna frat with one another, oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 You wouldn't be allowed to play with Catholic children?
