\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 He took you by surprise?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6565549 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 Yes. I got the surprise 
of my life. You ken, and I just - I says, yes, you and I'll go home. I says, well if you get in - and be in my company you'll behave yourself. So that was the finish.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 He didn't ask you to go out again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6565549 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 No. I'll bet he had a black eye because you
 see I was used - wrestling with my brothers here and - and - boxing. No, he - well he - I - I felt - I left nothing to chance. No, I just let go with my fist got in his - belt in his eye. 'Cos I knew nothing but - I - I didnae - I didnae know men got int
o that state. I didna - I thought men were gallant. I did. No, no, I looked on a man as a - for d\'e9
cor. Well years went by - years went by, I got married. He got married first. He - it was - anything - the chap was true enough, anything he told me was the tr
uth. He got married and he got married a second time, got a very nice wife. But we wasna married then but - we passed the house many time. Then I got married, and - I got a family, he got a family. And went to the seaside down at Kippford, that's a wee bi
t
 - we went down there. One - summer, we took rooms at Kippford and we just got this - you could go and take rooms then and you paid for your rooms and the folk cooked your food there, you see. Well - we were - werenae long into the rooms this night and my
 
husband would come down for the week - he was going to come down for the weekend and go back on the Monday. So - I looked out of the window and who was going past but this chap and his wife, and his bairns. Soon the Sunday - we went - along the shore and 
here his wife, him and his family. And we went - and his wains and our wains, they were all playing together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 
And your husband and his wife wouldn't know anything about you being out with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6565549 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 No. No. Here was - our wains and his wains were all p
laying together. And - then - he went away up on the Monday, he went back to his work, and his wife and I got very friendly. And she's a nice person. And we got very friendly. And - we spent the - enjoyed each other's company that holiday. And then she in
vited to come - to come down to see her - to come and see her. And I went to have my tea. See we cared nothing about it. But I just thought, well - wasn't it queer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 If she knew what you knew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6565549 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 Aye well - nobody knew anything about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 Did you breastfeed your first baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6565549 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 
Yes. At that time - that time - you - you fed your baby 'til it could have teeth. You didna feed it until it - you fed it and I don't know but - but they didnae feed them like what they do - what they do now.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 You didn't wean the baby nearly as quickly?
