e in the kitchen, yes. Cooked in the back kitchen, we cooked in the - well it was the back kitchen, did the cooking and - we ate in the kitchen, we lived in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 Is that this room here?
