 - for Christmas Day and high days and holidays. We werenae in that kind of - status.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid556246 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 But you would eat through there on special occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6565549 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 
Oh yes. Oh for special occasions you'd have the fire on and that, and Christmastime Oh yes, we'd always these places in Christmas time.
