 know whether - the boys'll - could remember. Oh I think we might have had the horse for - for one year anyway. Oh I was anxious for him to get a van because - when he worked for his other boss, oh he was out in all weathers. No shelter. You see? Oh I was
 
anxious for him to get the van. It let him get round, and then it was more comfortable. Oh he'd some terrible wettings - when - when - long ago, when he was with his other boss. Because - he'd the most antiquated vans, he'd never a new van, it was - ancie
nt looking things he used to have to - to sit on then.
