own property like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6565549 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322180\charrsid10313804 
Well he must have had - they must have had money or he must have had means. As I said, an engine driver was a good job then. You see? They were - they were - an engine driver - he would be considered to have a good job. He wou
ld be well paid. - Now - Miss Paddick that goes to St Mary's, that's his daughter. Do you know Miss Tannock? Oh well she - she's a great one going St Mary's. She lives out on {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}
}Locharbriggs Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. She's Tannock's daughter. Whether it was Tannock - and his - his wife used to -
